comment: Mills (SAS) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Ariza (HOU) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Ariza (HOU) and Mills (SAS) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court (2PT FGA) was upheld.
Ariza (HOU) makes contact with Leonard's (SAS) body that affects his jump shot attempt.
Ginobili (SAS) beats Ariza (HOU) to the spot and obtains a legal guarding position at the time of the contact.
Green (SAS) sets the screen on Ariza (HOU) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Harden (HOU) makes contact to Leonard's (SAS) foot that affects his driving shot attempt.
Harden (HOU) makes incidental contact with Green (SAS) that does not affect his FOM off ball.
Harden (HOU) is in the paint without actively guarding an opponent for longer than three seconds.
Aldridge (SAS) is in the paint for longer than three seconds.
Beverley (HOU) commits a take foul on Ginobili (SAS).
[Observable in production angle] Beverley (HOU) enters the area inside the three-point line prior to the free throw being released.
Simmons (SAS) makes incidental contact with Harden (HOU) that does not affect his FOM off ball.
Simmons (SAS) gives Harden (HOU) room to land following the jump shot attempt. Harden extends his leg and the contact is incidental.
